Industries


Investment Services & Portfolio Management




Company Description


Cornerstone Capital Management (CCM) is a large-cap growth investment manager. The firm's services include the management of US equity, US fixed-income and US balanced portfolios. CCM's selection of fixed-income investments is based on each client's investment objectives and risk tolerance and may include tax-exempt and/or taxable securities.CCM seeks to achieve long-term investment success for their clients by identifying underappreciated opportunities. The firm looks for high-quality, fundamentally strong companies with significant growth opportunities that are undervalued in the market. Stock selection is also based on the fundamentals of revenue, earnings, cash flow and the quality of management. Sector allocation is a by-product of individual stock selection. CCM invests mainly in stocks that are traded on the US exchanges or markets. The firm focuses on investments in the following sectors: (1) consumer (2) energy (3) financials (4) healthcare (5) industrials and (6) information technology.




