Head to Head Comparison: Synaptics (SYNA) versus ScanSource (SCSC)


					Posted by Lucas Kauffman on Jul 22nd, 2017 // No Comments




Synaptics (NASDAQ: SYNA) and ScanSource (NASDAQ:SCSC) are both small-cap computer and technology companies, but which is the better stock? We will contrast the two companies based on the strength of their profitabiliy, valuation, risk, analyst recommendations, institutional ownership, earnings and dividends. 
Profitability


